      m_Calls: []
  m_text: 'ATTENTION UNAUTHORIZED PASSENGER



    According to ship log #42, this
    vessel has been completely evacuated due to a "minor technical hiccup" (specifically,
    the main reactor turning into an impending supernova).



    As a stowaway,
    you were technically not on the manifest, meaning the automated escape system
    didn''t bother counting you. Don''t panic. Or do. Honestly, panicking is quite
    reasonable right now.



    The reactor will detonate in exactly 30 minutes,
    vaporizing this ship and, more importantly, destroying a perfectly good collection
    of digital tea leaves.



    Your task, assuming you wish to survive, is: Find
    the reactor, defuse the core, and try not to die.


    Note: You may request
    hints for the puzzles at any time. However, be advised that doing so will result
    in a penalty to your final score. Survival is rewarding, but efficiency is graded.'
