  m_Material: {fileID: 0}
  m_Color: {r: 1, g: 1, b: 1, a: 1}
  m_RaycastTarget: 1
  m_RaycastPadding: {x: 0, y: 0, z: 0, w: 0}
  m_Maskable: 1
  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: '


    ATTENTION UNAUTHORIZED PASSENGER


    This vessel has been completely
    evacuated due to a "minor technical hiccup" (specifically, the main reactor turning
    into an impending supernova).


    As a stowaway, you were technically not on
    the manifest, meaning the automated escape system didn''t bother counting you.
    Don''t panic. Or do. Honestly, panicking is quite reasonable right now.


    The
    reactor will detonate in exactly 30 minutes, vaporizing this ship and, more importantly,
    destroying a perfectly good collection of digital tea leaves.


    Your task,
    assuming you wish to survive, is: Find the reactor, defuse the core, and try
    not to die.


    Note: You may request hints for the puzzles at any time. However,
    be advised that doing so will result in a penalty to your final score.  To start
    your quest, interact with the hologram.


'
